%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9e7c527a6f66a8c49a6fab10a94681fc, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day4NightN
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  sequenceId: albert_day4_night_nopill
  lines:
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Evening, Andy. The logs show that the circuits by server room 1A are back
      online. How was it down there?
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: The work is the same as usual. Nothing super spectacular.
      nextLineIndex: 1
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "It\u2019s been\u2026 alright. Yeah, alright."
      nextLineIndex: 2
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "That\u2019s the spirit. An orderly day is a good day."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Are you sure? It seems like something is on your mind that\u2019s unrelated
      to our work here."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "I\u2019m okay. Just quite a few things on my mind right now. You
        don\u2019t have to worry about that."
      nextLineIndex: 3
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Anyhow, any burning questions you wanted to ask me before curfew?
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Weren\u2019t more passengers supposed to arrive on the ship? The
        place feels empty sometimes."
      nextLineIndex: 4
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: The DOLOS-XIII Management System. How do you view it all?The DOLOS-XIII
        Management System. How do you view it all?
      nextLineIndex: 7
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "Your daughter\u2026 what was her name? You didn\u2019t tell me
        this morning."
      nextLineIndex: 19
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "I think I\u2019m done asking questions tonight."
      nextLineIndex: 30
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 1
    advanceToLine: 30
    repeat: 1
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Last I checked, passenger rotations were delayed indefinitely. Corporate
      restructuring, I think.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 5
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: However, that was a few months ago.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 6
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "There\u2019s no need to pay it any mind now. Focusing on the main task
      at hand is your priority."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Ah. The DOLOS-XIII Management System is\u2026 well, it\u2019s nothing
      short of a monumental feat of engineering."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 8
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "The system is responsible for coordinating nearly everything on the ship.
      Life support, navigation, data collection, communications\u2026 it all runs
      through DOLOS-XIII."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 9
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: 'Of course, the company had previous iterations of the Management System.
      Albeit on a much smaller scale. Stuff like managing factories back on Earth. '
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 10
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: DOLOS-XIII, however, is the first designed for a fully habitable environment
      for a human crew.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 11
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "So far, it\u2019s been doing a flawless job."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Are there other versions? Newer models?
      nextLineIndex: 12
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: A few, yes.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 13
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "They run larger installations, like the Callisto mining colonies. I\u2019ve
      heard rumours of a DOLOS-XVI being developed for the \u201CErebus Initiative,\u201D
      but nobody knows what that is. Beyond my pay grade, that\u2019s certain."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 14
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Some corporations have tried to replicate DOLOS\u2019s source code. Competitors,
      foreign governments, and private military contractors, to name a few."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 15
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "They\u2019ve all failed."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 16
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "It\u2019s too complex\u2026 too unique. There are bogus online conspiracies
      that claim the source code was derived from something called \u201CProject
      Chimera,\u201D an old military program from the 2060s."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Project Chimera?
      nextLineIndex: 17
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Don\u2019t quote me on that, haha. The point of all that is, the DOLOS
      Management System is the crown jewel of the corporation."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 18
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "It\u2019s why Erebus Holdings acquired the DOLOS Corporation in the first
      place."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: albert_acquired
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "My daughter\u2026? Her name was R-Ro-Ros\u2026"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 20
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: '&*^@#*&^'
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 21
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 1
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: (*^@$#^*#&^!$$^
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 22
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 1
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: '[Error: Message goes beyond current parameters]'
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 23
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Apologies, my computer was malfunctioning for a moment. I had to run a
      diagnostic check in the background.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 2
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 24
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Everything is in the clear now, Andromeda. What were we talking about?
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "\u2026Nothing. We were talking about nothing."
      nextLineIndex: 25
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: Your daughter, Al. You mentioned you had one earlier today.
      nextLineIndex: 26
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Fair enough.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: I did?
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 27
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I\u2019ve never had a daughter."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 28
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Are you sure you\u2019re not hallucinating things? The capsule injections
      should be helping with that. You are taking them, right?"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Yeah\u2026 I have been\u2026"
      nextLineIndex: 29
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Excellent to hear. It\u2019s part of your contract to take them. You should
      never skip a dosage. Ever."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Night, Andy.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: -1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
    switchToDOLOS: 0
    glitch: 0
